Executive Profile
Joseph P. Mirabito  Chief Executive Officer, Mirabito Holdings, Inc.AgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 2 Board Members in 2 different organizations across 3 different industries.See Board Relationships58--
Background

		Mr. Joseph P. Mirabito, also known as Joe, has been the Chief Executive Officer at Mirabito Holdings, Inc. since 2009. Mr. Mirabito serves as Chief Executive Officer of Quickway Food Stores, Convenience Express and Mirabito Energy Products, Binghamton NY. He serves President of the Greater Sidney Development Corp. He serves on several professional and civic boards in the central New York region. He served as the President of Granite Capital Holdings, Inc. from 1998 to ... 2009. From 1986 to 1998, he held senior positions at Mirabito Fuel Group including President and Chief Executive Officer from 1996 to 1998. He serves as a Member of Advisory Board at ValueCentric Marketing Group, Inc. He has been a Director of the Empire State Petroleum Association since 2002 and Lemoyne College Board of Regents since 2004 and Corning Natural Gas Holding Corporation since 2013. Mr. Mirabito served as a Director at The Wilber Corporation since April 2005 and Wilber National Bank since 1995. He served as Director of the Otsego County Chamber of Commerce. He has been named the recipient of the 2010 Carl Tripi Award by the New York Association of Convenience Stores (NYACS). Mr. Mirabito is a Member of the National Association of Convenience Stores and Petroleum Marketers Association of America.Read Full Background




